arts.ttl: AFC Wimbledon vs Cardiff City: EFL League One Preview, Gameweek 4, 2025
arts.sum: Cardiff City make the trip to Plough Lane on Tuesday night as they look to extend their unbeaten start to the season against an AFC Wimbledon side buoyed by back-to-back victories. Rubin Colwill has been the standout performer, already netting three league goals this season, including a free-kick against Peterborough and a well-taken finish against Rotherham.
